{
  "title": "Business Metrics - EVE Online",
  "uid": "eve-business-metrics",
  "tags": ["business", "eve-online", "kills", "battles", "isk", "eve-copilot"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "time": {
    "from": "now-6h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "refresh": "1m",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 2,
  "templating": {
    "list": []
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Active Battles (Real-time)",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "eve_battles_active",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "green"
              },
              {
                "value": 50,
                "color": "yellow"
              },
              {
                "value": 100,
                "color": "orange"
              },
              {
                "value": 200,
                "color": "red"
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Battles Created (Total)",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 6,
        "y": 0
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(eve_battles_total)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Killmails Processed (Total)",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 0
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(eve_kills_total)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Kill Processing Rate",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 18,
        "y": 0
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "eve_kills_processing_rate",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "blue"
              },
              {
                "value": 1,
                "color": "green"
              },
              {
                "value": 5,
                "color": "yellow"
              },
              {
                "value": 10,
                "color": "red"
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "kills/s",
          "decimals": 2,
          "min": 0,
          "max": 20
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "showThresholdLabels": true,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Active Battles Over Time",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "eve_battles_active",
          "legendFormat": "Active Battles",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 20
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "none"
        },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": ["last", "mean", "max"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Battles Created by Region (Top 10)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "topk(10, sum(rate(eve_battles_total[5m])) by (region_name))",
          "legendFormat": "{{region_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 0
          },
          "unit": "battles/s",
          "min": 0
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": ["last", "mean", "max"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Killmail Processing Rate Over Time",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 14
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(eve_kills_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Total Kill Rate",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 10
          },
          "unit": "kills/s",
          "min": 0
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single"
        },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": ["last", "mean", "max"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "Top Attackers by Kill Count (Last 1h)",
      "type": "bargauge",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 14
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(increase(eve_kills_total[1h]))",
          "legendFormat": "Total Kills",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "displayMode": "gradient",
        "showUnfilled": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "title": "ISK Destroyed by Alliance (Top 10, Last 1h)",
      "type": "piechart",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 22
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(increase(eve_isk_destroyed_total[1h]))",
          "legendFormat": "ISK Destroyed",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 2
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "values": ["value", "percent"]
        },
        "pieType": "pie",
        "displayLabels": ["percent"]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "title": "ISK Lost by Alliance (Top 10, Last 1h)",
      "type": "piechart",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 22
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(increase(eve_isk_lost_total[1h]))",
          "legendFormat": "ISK Lost",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 2
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "values": ["value", "percent"]
        },
        "pieType": "pie",
        "displayLabels": ["percent"]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "title": "Future Business Metrics - Coming Soon",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 30
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Additional Business Metrics - Pending Instrumentation\n\n**Status**: 🟡 These metrics are defined but require service instrumentation.\n\n### Market Metrics\n- `eve_market_orders_total{character_id, order_type}` - Active market orders\n- `eve_market_volume_isk{character_id, region_id}` - Market order volume\n\n### Production Metrics\n- `eve_production_jobs{character_id, status}` - Production jobs (active/paused/delivered)\n- `eve_production_revenue_isk{character_id, activity_type}` - Production revenue\n\n### Character Metrics\n- `eve_character_assets_isk{character_id}` - Total asset value\n- `eve_wallet_balance_isk{character_id}` - Wallet balance\n- `eve_wallet_transactions_total{character_id, transaction_type}` - Transaction count\n\n**Next Step**: Instrument character-service, market-service, and production-service with business metrics."
      }
    }
  ]
}
